src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T06:58:51.000Z","msg":"淨係惡唔得,要賞罰分明,而且全家用同一個標準"},{"pid":"c7ff0aa6b9683d365e95574b045ccde97087c4f5","tid":1130462,"uid":17718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:17:10.000Z","msg":"我隻狗領養返黎個陣都好乖唔吠狗 耐左落街就吠狗 癲撚左咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8a68016098a506aa6004a70e97f71397de2cd6","tid":1130462,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:41:10.000Z","msg":"我聽過d 專業人士講，可能係訓得唔好，會影響佢平日日間活動，呢排訓覺環境有冇變化<br />\n<br />\n同埋可以抱佢落街，等佢聞到其他味，屈係屋企來來去去都係咁，人都癲"},{"pid":"f592a40c2b6b09948c92ce5063325cddae00ff65","tid":1130462,"uid":226612,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T17:27:12.000Z","msg":"我屋企隻poodle得閒就自己屋企9衝 <br />\n玩個陣都成日亂咬人知手 仲會惡<br />\n細細個個陣根本係癲 宜家就黎三歲已經冷靜左...小小<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba35efecf1a90528ac81403b6dcc58c24d130e3","tid":1130462,"uid":226612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T17:31:36.000Z","msg":"細個都係咁 買多啲磨牙野俾佢咬 多啲帶佢落街放電<br />\n咬你手一定要話佢 唔係大個會變習慣<br />\n我隻poodle細個個陣冇人係屋企真係拆屋咁款<br />\n翻到屋企全屋都係佢亂咬野既殘屑<br />\n細個都好唔鐘意人抱 一抱就扭<br />\n大左就正常啲 越黎越爹 成日要抱<br />\n不過都一定係好動架啦<br />\n對幼犬一定要有耐性 同埋獎罰分明<br />\n大個就會慢慢好"},{"pid":"0071d0b89c3e79aa60b3eeeb584e113ba3439a49","tid":1130462,"uid":203873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T12:26:15.000Z","msg":"有冇達人有啲好方法教下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家試緊搵繩綁住佢活動範圍<br />\n唔比佢亂走亂痴屎尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b0e1e52f5b7d784b27addf4c218c986d47227e","tid":1130462,"uid":203873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T12:26:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇達人有啲好方法教下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家試緊搵繩綁住佢活動範圍<br />\n唔比佢亂走亂痾屎尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"45e6b30bcf60bceca21cf61946616d7aaeb5ffda","tid":1130462,"uid":96068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T16:58:05.000Z","msg":"我屋企隻poodle乖到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由細到大都比較靜<br />\n教佢地我諗用野食同埋唔好成日搞佢<br />\n由得佢自己玩 做錯先鬧"}]}